{"tid":42681,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［十萬火急］有冇做開鎖佬嘅巴打可以教我點用萬字夾開呢種鎖？","createTime":"2016-12-17T01:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T03:03:55.000Z","uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"973ce5dcfb62debe7748b9636dbf7d1773e0bb6d","tid":42681,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:38:54.000Z","msg":"因為個學生擺左件冷衫係入面，但係我又冇帶鎖匙，焗住用萬字夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcAr8ej.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcAr8ej.jpg&h=32c8b9b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ffbeb5f53582112b836a8eb7ae1d9b8504ffa51","tid":42681,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:40:49.000Z","msg":"講你都學唔嚟啦 你估你考緊試呀 李克用呀李克強"},{"pid":"65133199a902b22db6e370fe3350fa48fbe4a4a3","tid":42681,"uid":18018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"畀返個櫃人啦"},{"pid":"cefd1be80416db3b4db36ae2ed5320660033284d","tid":42681,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講你都學唔嚟啦 你估你考緊試呀 李克用呀李克強</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實中學嘅時候試過開過，但事隔咁多年要重施故技真係好難，我又抆又插搞左好耐都未得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3855003854b2dce78b1d37395d0d9a608a9740d3","tid":42681,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畀返個櫃人啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"537e99c4bf3979e23575c79752a66c906f82b715","tid":42681,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"發夢見到應該要用兩條<br />\n一支頂/壓住個底<br />\n一支係上面可以下面果支為圓心黎轉<br />\n我係咁開<br />\n<br />\n有冇高手有其他高見"},{"pid":"5378ffc4e6470f0730985f5df9f5b90d3228926b","tid":42681,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:02:13.000Z","msg"